data.description: Everything comes together on this magnificent 10 acre property  in central florida among the rolling hills and glorious horse farms the area is known for.  This stately 4 bedroom 3 1/2 bath home offers the perfect country setting for you.  Enjoy and  appreciate the subtle touches throughout the home. A wood burning fireplace graces your living room and sits adjacent to a private en suite with a  full bathroom and separate  entrance.  Master bedroom has trey ceilings, two skylights which allows for plenty of natural light and 2 ample his and her walk in  closets.  A split floor plan allows for easy and enjoyable, private entertaining as there are 2 guest bedrooms with a jack and jill bathroom off the main living  area.  Hosting family and friends will be a breeze from your large living room with quick access to the kitchen. You will be pleased to have 2 pantries,  granite countertops and  a well situated island. A breakfast bar proves to be an added extra bonus for friends and family who choose to stay close to the chef of the house as plans and events of the day are made.  Working from home or just needing some space to carry out  normal everyday business just got easier with a quiet office area near the front of the house.  From the back of the house you will notice a lovely covered lanai where you can relax and breathe deeply after a full day.  Your horses will love the center -aisle barn with 8 stalls.  Everything has been thought of from the tack room with AC to the 4 boarded paddocks with  waterers and lets not forget the icing on the cake------the ARENA! Towards the back of the property near the tree line is a very large equipment storage area just right for storing tools and all the other machinery you will use on this 10 acre piece of paradise .  Come and train year round while enjoying plenty of privacy.  The World Equestrian Center is approximately 9 - 10 miles away as is the Jockey Club and HITS.  Within your easy reach is the Equine Medical Center of Ocala, Ocala Equine Hospital and Ferguson & Associates Equine Hospital not to mention the renowned  and easily accessible University of Florida Large Animal Hospital.  Life will only get better once you call this 10 acre farm HOME.
